If you get a 0-value item from combining, 'scissors' can sometimes raise it to 50, but it's risky and might result in negative values, especially with 'hard' items. Avoid applying a second tool to an item that already has one tool applied, as this almost always leads to significantly negative values. Aim for a 50 or 70 and then submit to protect your score.
